summary: Adds crystal skulls to the game.
descriptionHtml:
MurdermiesteR here again with a pointless mod that I made after too many Youtube videos. Interesting fact; we don't actually know a single real thing about them except that they are skulls made of crystal. Everything else is he said or I heard stories. They cost nothing to craft. Make a million and fill a house with them. Make a mountain or fill a lake. I made 2 and tastefully placed them in my favorite flats. Enjoy and feel free to use in your home mod or whatnot.
